-khuluq","tag-hypocrisy-al-nifaq","tag-manners-adab","tag-refuge-al-taawwudh","tag-supplication-al-dua"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-aJI","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":34032,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/03\/01\/refuge-physical-mental-illness\/","url_meta":{"origin":41274,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Disease: Seek refuge in Allah from physical, mental illness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 1, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in you from leprosy, madness, contagion, and evil ailments.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1554 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u064e\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38383,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/24\/prophet-refuge-injustice\/","url_meta":{"origin":41274,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet seeks refuge from committing injustice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 24, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from poverty, scarcity, and humiliation. I seek refuge in You from committing wrong or being wronged.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1544 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34131,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/21\/dua-fear-evil-people\/","url_meta":{"origin":41274,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Supplication if afraid of bad people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, feared evil from people, he would say, \u201cO Allah, we place You in front of them, and we seek refuge in You from their evil.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 1537 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Nawawi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13739,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/25\/security-asks-bismillah\/","url_meta":{"origin":41274,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Security: Grant refuge to whoever asks by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever seeks refuge with you in the name of Allah, grant him refuge. Whoever asks you in the name of Allah, give it to him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 5109 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33028,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/seek-refuge-entering-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":41274,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from Satan when entering mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the mosque, he would say, \u201cI seek refuge in Allah Almighty, in his noble countenance, and in his everlasting authority from the accursed Satan.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 466 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25346,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/28\/dua-refuge-bad-character\/","url_meta":{"origin":41274,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: I seek refuge in Allah from bad character","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 28, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Qutbah ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in you from evil character traits, evil deeds, and evil desires.\u